===Particle===
'''きり''' (''kiri'')

# just, only
#: More rarely used than [[丈]] ([[だけ]], ''dake''), [[切り]] (きり, ''kiri'') functions as a noun and may be followed by [[の]] (''no'').  
#* [[二人]]'''きり'''のお[[店]]
#*:[[ふたり]]'''きり'''のお[[みせ]]
#*:''[[futari]] '''kiri''' no o-[[mise]]''
#*:a [[shop]] with '''just''' [[two]] [[people]] [who work there]

